  <span id="freeText10992726017530243047" style="display:none">These are interesting stories and heart touching. When I read them, I couldn't put the book down and was haunted by some of them after.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10992726017530243047" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

